{"tid":494115,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)希魔撞正殺人狂","createTime":"2017-12-09T09:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T11:32:34.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f1fdd6738b98feb864186c72f93617d7b6c6edb9","tid":494115,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:20:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Cm8rMD9sWM3SSTfCICCbrLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=f2906eb4\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Cm8rMD9sWM3SSTfCICCbrLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=64af232d\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/81/Inglourious_Basterds_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F81%2FInglourious_Basterds_Poster.jpg&h=90efad21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在二次大戰期間德占區的法國，外號「猶太獵人」（The Jew Hunter）的親衛隊上校漢斯&middot;蘭達（Hans Landa，克里斯多夫&middot;華茲飾）在一位法國奶農皮埃爾&middot;拉帕提（Perrier LaPadite）的家中審問他。拉帕提為了家人的安全供認了猶太裔的德瑞芙斯（Dreyfus）一家就藏在他家的地板下。蘭達讓親衛隊士兵隔著地板掃射殺害了這一家人，但少女蘇珊娜（Shosanna，梅蘭妮&middot;羅蘭飾）僥倖逃脫。<br />\n1944年春，美國第一特種部隊的艾杜連中尉（First Lieutenant Aldo Raine，布萊德&middot;彼特飾）招募了8名美國猶太人士兵來完成一項敵後任務，說他們每人欠他100張納粹頭皮，並且不收俘虜。他們被稱為「惡棍特工」。阿道夫&middot;希特勒私下詢問了一名叫布茨的士兵，他講述了自己的小隊是如何遭惡棍特工伏擊，他的中士拒絕泄露情報後如何被綽號「猶太熊」（Bear Jew）的唐尼&middot;唐諾維茲中士（Sgt. Donny Donowitz，伊萊&middot;羅斯飾）用棒球棍活活打死。布茨因透露情報而倖免於難，但艾杜連在他額頭上用刀刻了一個卐<br />\n<br />\n5 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  播完播返HERO2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Cm8rMD9sWM3SSTfCICCbrLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=174123b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Cm8rMD9sWM3SSTfCICCbrLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=a1785905\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcba476a1ebe15a0295de89f6e47bb2c1b8ceef5","tid":494115,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32851580d21292f9ee83be314b72f80ce5375f69","tid":494115,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T10:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f60d2bce2bf8dc3c78a8c21feb355ebeda62687","tid":494115,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T11:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}